flowchart TB
    Client([Client])
    UploadEdge[Upload Edge]
    ObjectStore[(Object Store<br/>raw + transcoded)]
    Transcoder[Transcoder<br/>240p / 480p / 720p<br/>+ thumbnail]
    CDN[(CDN<br/>HLS / MP4 manifests)]
    MetaDB[(Video Metadata<br/>wide-column)]
    FeedSvc[Feed Service<br/>For You]
    RecSvc[Recommendation Service<br/>two-tower retrieval<br/>+ multi-task ranker]
    Embeddings[(Embedding Store<br/>user + video vectors)]
    Interactions[(Interaction Stream<br/>watch / like / share)]

    Client -->|upload| UploadEdge
    UploadEdge --> ObjectStore
    ObjectStore -.->|trigger| Transcoder
    Transcoder --> CDN
    Transcoder --> MetaDB
    Client -->|swipe| FeedSvc
    FeedSvc --> RecSvc
    RecSvc <--> Embeddings
    FeedSvc --> MetaDB
    FeedSvc -->|manifest URLs| CDN
    CDN -->|video chunks| Client
    Client -.->|watch events| Interactions
    Interactions -.->|train| RecSvc

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class UploadEdge,Transcoder,FeedSvc,RecSvc service
    class ObjectStore,CDN,MetaDB,Embeddings,Interactions store
